Package seng201.team005.models

Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
seng201.team005.models.Purchasable
seng201.team005.models.Car
seng201.team005.models.Entrant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Entrant>
public class Entrant extends Car implements Comparable<Entrant>
Represents an entrant in a race, extending the Car class and implementing the Comparable interface. This class tracks the entrant's progress, fuel, position, and status during the race.
